name: details in the fabric #3
description:
collection I did during summers vacation job in the fabric - these days are over where people spend 1/4 of their entire life in a fabric, doing a job that a machine could do better - dreamy but possible, everybody is stoic, don’t buy bullshit, don’t shower every day for 15mins, just get aware that ressources aren’t infinite, supporting art is the direction #stakeholdercapitalism
made with an Iphone12, 7.7 MB, edited with Lightroom
